&lt;h3 id=&#34;advanced-features&#34;&gt;Advanced Features&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flexible Language Support&lt;/strong&gt;: Add as many languages as needed in multilingual format&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fallback System&lt;/strong&gt;: Uses default name if specific language is not found&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Weight-based Sorting&lt;/strong&gt;: Control category order in navigation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more details, check the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/your-theme/docs&#34;&gt;theme documentation&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
